tc_game_scripts.description: Download Latest Torch API after Steam Update
tc_game_scripts.script_contents:
import clr clr.AddReference('System.IO.Compression.FileSystem') clr.AddReference("TCAdmin.SDK") from System.IO import Directory, File from System.Net import WebClient from TCAdmin.SDK.Misc import CompressionTools
c=CompressionTools() Script.WriteToConsole('Checking if Space Engineers exe exists') # Check if space engineers exe is valid if File.Exists(ThisService.RootDirectory + 'DedicatedServer64/SpaceEngineersDedicated.exe'): if File.Exists(ThisService.RootDirectory + 'torch-server.zip'): File.Delete(ThisService.RootDirectory + 'torch-server.zip')
Script.WriteToConsole('Downloading Latest Version of Torch API...') url = "https://build.torchapi.com/job/Torch/job/master/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/bin/torch-server.zip" fileName = ThisService.RootDirectory + "torch-server.zip" wc = WebClient() Script.WriteToConsole("Downloading File " + fileName + " from " + url +"...\n\n") wc.DownloadFile(url,fileName)
Script.WriteToConsole("Extracting " + fileName) if File.Exists(ThisService.RootDirectory + 'torch-server.zip'): c.Decompress(ThisService.RootDirectory + "torch-server.zip", ThisService.RootDirectory) File.Delete(ThisService.RootDirectory + 'torch-server.zip') else: Script.WriteToConsole('Error: Downloading Torch API. Please contact support')

import clr clr.AddReference("System.Xml")
from System import Exception from System import String from System.IO import Path from System.Xml import XmlDocument
# First Configuration Path configpath1 = Path.Combine(ThisService.RootDirectory, "Instance/Saves/world/Sandbox.sbc") xmldoc1 = XmlDocument() xmldoc1.Load(configpath1)
mods1 = xmldoc1.SelectSingleNode("MyObjectBuilder_Checkpoint/Mods") if mods1 is None: raise Exception("Could not find Mods section in the first configuration")
# Add only if mod does not exist modinfo1 = mods1.SelectSingleNode(String.Format("ModItem[PublishedFileId='{0}']", FileId)) if modinfo1 is None: modinfo1 = xmldoc1.CreateElement("ModItem") modname1 = xmldoc1.CreateElement("Name") modfileid1 = xmldoc1.CreateElement("PublishedFileId") modname1.InnerText=String.Format("{0}.sbm", FileId) modfileid1.InnerText=FileId.ToString() modinfo1.AppendChild(modname1) modinfo1.AppendChild(modfileid1) mods1.AppendChild(modinfo1) xmldoc1.Save(configpath1)
# Second Configuration Path configpath2 = Path.Combine(ThisService.RootDirectory, "Instance/Saves/world/Sandbox_config.sbc") xmldoc2 = XmlDocument() xmldoc2.Load(configpath2)
mods2 = xmldoc2.SelectSingleNode("MyObjectBuilder_WorldConfiguration/Mods") if mods2 is None: raise Exception("Could not find Mods section in the second configuration")
# Add only if mod does not exist modinfo2 = mods2.SelectSingleNode(String.Format("ModItem[PublishedFileId='{0}']", FileId)) if modinfo2 is None: modinfo2 = xmldoc2.CreateElement("ModItem") modname2 = xmldoc2.CreateElement("Name") modfileid2 = xmldoc2.CreateElement("PublishedFileId") modname2.InnerText=String.Format("{0}.sbm", FileId) modfileid2.InnerText=FileId.ToString() modinfo2.AppendChild(modname2) modinfo2.AppendChild(modfileid2) mods2.AppendChild(modinfo2) xmldoc2.Save(configpath2)
